%85%a5%e6%94%bf%e6%b2%bb%e3%80%8d-%e9%be%8d%e6%8c%af%e9%82%a6%e8%a2%81%e5%9c%8b%e5%8b%87%e6%92%a4%e5%9b%9e%e6%96%87%e7%ab%a0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「追求科學真理　無意捲入政治」　龍振邦袁國勇撤回文章 <br />\n<br />\n本報觀點版今日刊登香港大學李嘉誠醫學院微生物學系名譽助理教授龍振邦，及香港大學李嘉誠醫學院霍英東基金（傳染病學）教授袁國勇來稿〈大流行緣起武漢 十七年教訓盡忘〉，龍振邦及袁國勇現撤回文章。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n龍振邦及袁國勇表示，他們是科學家，終身追求科學真理，不了解政治，也從來無意捲入政治。「文章表達不適當，用詞甚至有錯誤，並非原意，希望外界不要把我們捲入政治，留給我們一個空間研究。」<br />\n<br />\n他們稱，該文與政治無關，旨在提出尊重真相、移風易俗。若當中的手民之誤引起任何誤會，龍振邦及袁國勇表示歉意。"},{"pid":"6944d10f07be1caa18897f36b6a07977e6e36d14","tid":1932322,"uid":79117,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cc7828f7640a6934d54ce10270a2fb6078608b","tid":1932322,"uid":146030,"like":6,"dislike":73,"score":-67,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:59:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823809f94b82dfb12233507682b9341cf7531849","tid":1932322,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbd951f4eaa7670afb999a01c32d0166334605f","tid":1932322,"uid":41389,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"做人最緊要有尊嚴"},{"pid":"acde87ccb11706ee7d5cbe560ab1f224b0aff387","tid":1932322,"uid":79117,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"而家邊個搞文革啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414d68b72468f362719749e2b7c5ccec768e7573","tid":1932322,"uid":278712,"like":146,"dislike":0,"score":146,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375cc161a4e191eaedd72a65241315f94c57630c